Proto dropped down about a 100 yards from the battle. He transformed into his 
silvery form. It looks like a protoform exactly just his spark isnt exposed.  
He hardened his skin into solid metal. Spikes shot from his elbows shoulders 
and hands. Long stings of silver metal shot from his head to make what looked 
like hair. Red orbs where located where his eyes were. This is what proto 
chose to think of himself looking like. It was his perfered shape when not in 
animal mode. He looked back.."So....who do you suppose we help. If i 
understand this correctly I am scanning two pred tribes here."

--part1_15c.fbed444.2a531eae_boundary
